  "instructions_to_main_agent": "You are building a Tambola Game. Focus on the 'Live Game' experience. The ticket grid is the most important component. It must be responsive and easy to tap. Use the provided colors to create a festive but usable dark mode interface. Use the 'Outfit' font for headings to give it a modern feel. Implement the 'My Tickets' section with a clear distinction between 'Upcoming' and 'Past' games."
